      • addSessionCatalog

        public void addSessionCatalog(java.lang.String id)
        The IDs of catalogs that should be updated with session information (plays, skips, ratings,bans, favorites, etc). Multiple session catalogs (up to 5) can be listed and all will be updated with the same information. The session catalogs must have been previously created using the same API key as used in this call.
        Parameters:
        id - the session catalog to add
